---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = '2026-06-27';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | calorie.monster" description="Privacy policy, cookies and advertising for calorie.monster." lang="en" canonicalPath="/en/privacy">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
    <p>calorie.monster provides food nutrition and calorie search without accounts or logins. Your searches and page views are not stored on a server, and we do not collect information that identifies you personally.</p>

    <h2>2. Cookies & local storage</h2>
    <p>We may use cookies to improve your experience and collect usage statistics. You can block cookies in your browser settings; some features may be limited as a result.</p>

    <h2>3. Google AdSense (ads)</h2>
    <p>Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visit. You may opt out of personalized advertising at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" rel="nofollow">Google Ads Settings</a> or <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" rel="nofollow">aboutads.info</a>.</p>

    <h2>4. Usage statistics (Google Analytics)</h2>
    <p>We use Google Analytics to collect usage statistics to improve the service. The data is anonymized and is not used to identify individuals. Google may set cookies for this data; you can block cookies in your browser settings. See the <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/cookies" rel="nofollow">Google cookie policy</a> and the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="nofollow">Google Analytics opt-out add-on</a>.</p>

    <h2>5. Data sources</h2>
    <p>Nutrition data is based on the <a href="https://fdc.nal.usda.gov/" rel="nofollow">USDA FoodData Central</a> (U.S. public domain) and the 식약처 food nutrition database (Korean public data, no use restrictions). Each food page credits its source.</p>

    <h2>6. Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>Nutrition information on this site is for reference only and is not medical or nutritional advice.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:core13773@gmail.com">core13773@gmail.com</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
<style>.prose{max-width:720px;line-height:1.7}.prose h2{margin-top:1.6rem;font-size:1.1rem}.prose p{color:var(--prose)}</style>
